          ></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@alec.j" target="_blank">
        <span class="sr-only">Subscribe to Alec Jensen on YouTube</span>
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
